headline: What the $1 trillion rural wallet means for Walmart, Amazon
summary: The battle for rural consumers is heating up, and major US companies are investing heavily to win the country road.

headline: My 3 Favorite Stocks to Buy Right Now
summary: Stocks are benefiting from a resilient economy and strong corporate earnings.  Investors can still find plenty of attractive opportunities in the market by focusing on high-quality companies with long-term growth potential.  Shares of Carnival, Dollar Tree, and Dell Technologies could be big winners into the second half of the year.
